How to set this project up in QtCreator (2.6)
---------------------------------------------
1. File | Open File or Project...
2. Browse to "CMakeLists.txt" in opm-verteq.
   Open.
3. Build directory: /home/rka081/opm/bld/opm-verteq
   Next.
4. Arguments: -DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=Debug -Dopm-core_DIR=«path-to-opm-core» -DPRECOMPILE_HEADERS=ON -DBUILD_SHARED_LIBS=ON
   Run CMake
   Finish
5. Projects (on the sidebar)
6. Build Steps
   Details
   Targets: [X] opmverteq
7. Build | Build All
